  "prompt": "How do I send my message from Facebook to WhatsApp?",
  "response": "To send a message from Facebook to WhatsApp, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. Open the Facebook Messenger conversation\n2. Click on the message you want to share\n3. Select the \"Forward\" option\n4. Choose WhatsApp as the destination\n5. Select the contact or group you want to send the message to\n6. Hit send\n\nAlternatively, you can:\n- Copy the message text\n- Open WhatsApp\n- Paste the message in a new chat\n\nNote: The exact steps might vary slightly depending on your device (mobile/desktop) and the specific versions of Facebook Messenger and WhatsApp you're using.",
